    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "What I found is that clicking in the slider should add a class to the handle but fails because the reference to the handle (`data.handles[0]`) is `undefined`. \n\nAs this is using a forked version of nouislider, wrapped in our own React component widget I kind of lost the track of the origing of it. Maybe someone more used to the slider could have a look?\n",
